				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>My suggestion: begin by stepping only on red blocks, to get to the below:</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-146" src="../wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-214226-576x1024.png" alt="" width="576" height="1024" srcset="http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-214226-576x1024.png 576w, http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-214226-169x300.png 169w, http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-214226-768x1365.png 768w, http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-214226.png 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px" /></p>
<p>Then clear out 6 yellow tiles:</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-147" src="../wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-214249-576x1024.png" alt="" width="576" height="1024" srcset="http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-214249-576x1024.png 576w, http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-214249-169x300.png 169w, http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-214249-768x1365.png 768w, http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-214249.png 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px" /></p>
<p>The rest shouldn&#8217;t be too bad.</p>
