	<article id="post-138" class="post-138 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-strategy-and-hints">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="../medium-5.html" rel="bookmark">Medium &#8211; 5</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="../medium-5.html" title="3:10 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2017-07-03T15:10:52+00:00">July 3, 2017</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="../author/star-scythe_8.html" title="View all posts by Silent Zebra" rel="author">Silent Zebra</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
						<div class="comments-link">
				<a href="../medium-5.html#respond"><span class="leave-reply">Reply</span></a>			</div>
					</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>There are many solutions to this level. My preferred path begins with moving right first, then up, clearing the top area until you get to the below position:</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-139" src="../wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-213520-576x1024.png" alt="" width="576" height="1024" srcset="http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-213520-576x1024.png 576w, http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-213520-169x300.png 169w, http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-213520-768x1365.png 768w, http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-213520.png 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px" /></p>
<p>Then clear the row below, getting to this position:</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-140" src="../wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-213732-576x1024.png" alt="" width="576" height="1024" srcset="http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-213732-576x1024.png 576w, http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-213732-169x300.png 169w, http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-213732-768x1365.png 768w, http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-213732.png 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px" /></p>
<p>The rest should be fairly straightforward. You can use the principle of working from the outside in, looping around the outside first.</p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
