	<article id="post-134" class="post-134 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-strategy-and-hints">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="../medium-4.html" rel="bookmark">Medium &#8211; 4</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="../medium-4.html" title="3:10 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2017-07-03T15:10:45+00:00">July 3, 2017</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="../author/star-scythe_8.html" title="View all posts by Silent Zebra" rel="author">Silent Zebra</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
						<div class="comments-link">
				<a href="../medium-4.html#respond"><span class="leave-reply">Reply</span></a>			</div>
					</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Go straight up from the beginning, to the top. There are multiple paths from then on.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-289" src="../wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170729-213817-576x1024.png" alt="" width="576" height="1024" srcset="http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170729-213817-576x1024.png 576w, http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170729-213817-169x300.png 169w, http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170729-213817-768x1365.png 768w, http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170729-213817.png 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px" /></p>
<p>The inspiration for this level was a &#8220;figure 8&#8221;.</p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
												<span class="cat-links">
