	<article id="post-131" class="post-131 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-strategy-and-hints">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="../medium-3.html" rel="bookmark">Medium &#8211; 3</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="../medium-3.html" title="3:10 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2017-07-03T15:10:37+00:00">July 3, 2017</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="../author/star-scythe_8.html" title="View all posts by Silent Zebra" rel="author">Silent Zebra</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
						<div class="comments-link">
				<a href="../medium-3.html#respond"><span class="leave-reply">Reply</span></a>			</div>
					</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>After the first move (which is forced), move to the left and clear off that section fully first. You should get to the below position:</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-132" src="../wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-212004-576x1024.png" alt="" width="576" height="1024" srcset="http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-212004-576x1024.png 576w, http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-212004-169x300.png 169w, http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-212004-768x1365.png 768w, http://silentzebra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screenshot_20170630-212004.png 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px" /></p>
<p>Then, move down. Leave the top six squares for last (they are the &#8220;<a href="../general-strategy-ends.html">end</a>&#8220;).</p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
												<span class="cat-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="../category/strategy-and-hints" rel="category tag">Strategy and Hints</a>			</span>
															
